        * Removed support for Django 1.7
        
        
        1.0.0 (2016-01-23)
        ------------------
        
        * First release on PyPI.
        * ``I200`` rule that complains about unnecessary import aliasing, e.g.
          ``from foo import bar as bar``.
        
